{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"When I was 10 years old,"},{"time":4000,"text":"a cousin of mine took me on a tour of his medical school."},{"time":7000,"text":"And as a special treat,"},{"time":9000,"text":"he took me to the pathology lab"},{"time":11000,"text":"and took a real human brain"},{"time":13000,"text":"out of the jar"},{"time":15000,"text":"and placed it in my hands."},{"time":17000,"text":"And there it was,"},{"time":19000,"text":"the seat of human consciousness,"},{"time":21000,"text":"the powerhouse of the human body,"},{"time":23000,"text":"sitting in my hands."},{"time":25000,"text":"And that day I knew that when I grew up,"},{"time":27000,"text":"I was going to become a brain doctor,"},{"time":29000,"text":"scientist, something or the other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32000,"text":"Years later, when I finally grew up,"},{"time":35000,"text":"my dream came true."},{"time":37000,"text":"And it was while I was doing my Ph.D."},{"time":39000,"text":"on the neurological causes"},{"time":41000,"text":"of dyslexia in children"},{"time":43000,"text":"that I encountered a startling fact"},{"time":45000,"text":"that I'd like to share with you all today."},{"time":49000,"text":"It is estimated that one in six children,"},{"time":51000,"text":"that's one in six children,"},{"time":54000,"text":"suffer from some developmental disorder."},{"time":58000,"text":"This is a disorder that"},{"time":60000,"text":"retards mental development in the child"},{"time":62000,"text":"and causes permanent mental impairments."},{"time":66000,"text":"Which means that each and every one of you here today"},{"time":69000,"text":"knows at least one child that is suffering"},{"time":72000,"text":"from a developmental disorder."}]},{"cues":[{"time":75000,"text":"But here's what really perplexed me."},{"time":77000,"text":"Despite the fact that each"},{"time":79000,"text":"and every one of these disorders"},{"time":81000,"text":"originates in the brain,"},{"time":84000,"text":"most of these disorders"},{"time":86000,"text":"are diagnosed solely on the basis"},{"time":88000,"text":"of observable behavior."},{"time":91000,"text":"But diagnosing a brain disorder"},{"time":93000,"text":"without actually looking at the brain"},{"time":96000,"text":"is analogous to treating a patient with a heart problem"},{"time":99000,"text":"based on their physical symptoms,"},{"time":101000,"text":"without even doing an ECG or a chest X-ray"},{"time":104000,"text":"to look at the heart."},{"time":106000,"text":"It seemed so intuitive to me."},{"time":109000,"text":"To diagnose and treat a brain disorder accurately,"},{"time":112000,"text":"it would be necessary to look at the brain directly."},{"time":115000,"text":"Looking at behavior alone"},{"time":117000,"text":"can miss a vital piece of the puzzle"},{"time":120000,"text":"and provide an incomplete, or even a misleading,"},{"time":123000,"text":"picture of the child's problems."},{"time":126000,"text":"Yet, despite all the advances in medical technology,"},{"time":129000,"text":"the diagnosis of brain disorders"},{"time":131000,"text":"in one in six children"},{"time":133000,"text":"still remained so limited."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137000,"text":"And then I came across a team at Harvard University"},{"time":140000,"text":"that had taken one such advanced medical technology"},{"time":143000,"text":"and finally applied it,"},{"time":145000,"text":"instead of in brain research,"},{"time":147000,"text":"towards diagnosing brain disorders in children."},{"time":151000,"text":"Their groundbreaking technology"},{"time":153000,"text":"records the EEG, or the electrical activity"},{"time":156000,"text":"of the brain, in real time,"},{"time":159000,"text":"allowing us to watch the brain"},{"time":161000,"text":"as it performs various functions"},{"time":164000,"text":"and then detect even the slightest abnormality"},{"time":166000,"text":"in any of these functions:"},{"time":168000,"text":"vision, attention, language, audition."},{"time":171000,"text":"A program called Brain Electrical"},{"time":173000,"text":"Activity Mapping"},{"time":175000,"text":"then triangulates the source"},{"time":177000,"text":"of that abnormality in the brain."},{"time":179000,"text":"And another program called"},{"time":181000,"text":"Statistical Probability Mapping"},{"time":183000,"text":"then performs mathematical calculations"},{"time":186000,"text":"to determine whether any of these abnormalities"},{"time":188000,"text":"are clinically significant,"},{"time":190000,"text":"allowing us to provide a much more accurate"},{"time":192000,"text":"neurological diagnosis"},{"time":194000,"text":"of the child's symptoms."},{"time":196000,"text":"And so I became the head of neurophysiology"},{"time":199000,"text":"for the clinical arm of this team,"},{"time":201000,"text":"and we're finally able to use this technology"},{"time":203000,"text":"towards actually helping"},{"time":205000,"text":"children with brain disorders."},{"time":207000,"text":"And I'm happy to say that I'm now in the process"},{"time":209000,"text":"of setting up this technology here in India."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213000,"text":"I'd like to tell you about one such child,"},{"time":216000,"text":"whose story was also covered by ABC News."},{"time":220000,"text":"Seven-year-old Justin Senigar"},{"time":222000,"text":"came to our clinic with this diagnosis"},{"time":224000,"text":"of very severe autism."},{"time":226000,"text":"Like many autistic children,"},{"time":228000,"text":"his mind was locked inside his body."},{"time":231000,"text":"There were moments when he would"},{"time":233000,"text":"actually space out for seconds at a time."},{"time":236000,"text":"And the doctors told his parents"},{"time":238000,"text":"he was never going to be able"},{"time":240000,"text":"to communicate or interact socially,"},{"time":242000,"text":"and he would probably never have too much language."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"When we used this groundbreaking EEG technology"},{"time":249000,"text":"to actually look at Justin's brain,"},{"time":252000,"text":"the results were startling."},{"time":255000,"text":"It turned out that Justin was almost"},{"time":257000,"text":"certainly not autistic."},{"time":259000,"text":"He was suffering from brain seizures"},{"time":262000,"text":"that were impossible to see with the naked eye,"},{"time":265000,"text":"but that were actually causing symptoms"},{"time":267000,"text":"that mimicked those of autism."},{"time":270000,"text":"After Justin was given anti-seizure medication,"},{"time":273000,"text":"the change in him was amazing."},{"time":276000,"text":"Within a period of 60 days,"},{"time":278000,"text":"his vocabulary went from two to three words"},{"time":281000,"text":"to 300 words."},{"time":283000,"text":"And his communication and social interaction"},{"time":285000,"text":"were improved so dramatically"},{"time":287000,"text":"that he was enrolled into a regular school"},{"time":290000,"text":"and even became a karate super champ."}]},{"cues":[{"time":294000,"text":"Research shows that 50 percent of children,"},{"time":296000,"text":"almost 50 percent of children"},{"time":298000,"text":"diagnosed with autism"},{"time":300000,"text":"are actually suffering from hidden brain seizures."},{"time":305000,"text":"These are the faces of the children"},{"time":307000,"text":"that I have tested"},{"time":309000,"text":"with stories just like Justin."},{"time":312000,"text":"All these children"},{"time":314000,"text":"came to our clinic with a diagnosis"},{"time":316000,"text":"of autism, attention deficit disorder,"},{"time":319000,"text":"mental retardation, language problems."},{"time":323000,"text":"Instead, our EEG scans revealed"},{"time":326000,"text":"very specific problems hidden within their brains"},{"time":329000,"text":"that couldn't possibly have been detected"},{"time":331000,"text":"by their behavioral assessments."},{"time":334000,"text":"So these EEG scans"},{"time":336000,"text":"enabled us to provide these children"},{"time":338000,"text":"with a much more accurate neurological diagnosis"},{"time":341000,"text":"and much more targeted treatment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345000,"text":"For too long now, children with developmental disorders"},{"time":348000,"text":"have suffered from misdiagnosis"},{"time":350000,"text":"while their real problems have gone undetected"},{"time":352000,"text":"and left to worsen."},{"time":354000,"text":"And for too long, these children and their parents"},{"time":357000,"text":"have suffered undue frustration and desperation."},{"time":360000,"text":"But we are now in a new era of neuroscience,"},{"time":363000,"text":"one in which we can finally look"},{"time":366000,"text":"directly at brain function in real time"},{"time":369000,"text":"with no risks and no side effects, non-invasively,"},{"time":372000,"text":"and find the true source"},{"time":374000,"text":"of so many disabilities in children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377000,"text":"So if I could inspire"},{"time":379000,"text":"even a fraction of you in the audience today"},{"time":382000,"text":"to share this pioneering diagnostic approach"},{"time":385000,"text":"with even one parent whose child"},{"time":387000,"text":"is suffering from a developmental disorder,"},{"time":390000,"text":"then perhaps one more puzzle"},{"time":392000,"text":"in one more brain will be solved."},{"time":394000,"text":"One more mind will be unlocked."},{"time":396000,"text":"And one more child who has been misdiagnosed"},{"time":398000,"text":"or even undiagnosed by the system"},{"time":401000,"text":"will finally realize his or her true potential"},{"time":404000,"text":"while there's still time"},{"time":406000,"text":"for his or her brain to recover."},{"time":408000,"text":"And all this by simply watching the child's brainwaves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":413000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}